DESCRIPTION: Enhances the draggable chess piece by adding state management to provide visual feedback during dragging. When dragged, the piece's opacity is reduced to make it appear as if it's being picked up.
SOURCE: https://github.com/atlassian/pragmatic-drag-and-drop/blob/main/packages/documentation/constellation/01-tutorial/index.mdx#2025-04-14_snippet_1

