TITLE: External Data Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Example demonstrating how to configure external data for drag operations, including task details and URL formatting.
SOURCE: https://github.com/atlassian/pragmatic-drag-and-drop/blob/main/packages/documentation/constellation/05-core-package/00-adapters/00-element/about.mdx#2025-04-14_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { formatURLsForExternal } from '@atlaskit/pragmatic-drag-and-drop/element/format-urls-for-external';

draggable({
	element: myElement,
	getInitialData: () => ({ taskId: task.id }),
	getInitialDataForExternal: () => ({
		'text/plain': task.description,
		'text/uri-list': formatURLsForExternal([task.url, task.anotherUrl]),
	}),
});
```

